OL,3,CTwo men arrested after teenager
OL,4,Ccritically injured in Bradford hit-and-
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FTwo men have been arrested in
OL,8,Fconnection with a hit-and-run in
OL,9,FBradford which has left a teenager in
OL,10,Fhospital in critical condition.
OL,12,FThe 17-year-old boy suffered serious
OL,13,Finjuries after being hit by a car seen
OL,14,Fspeeding in Bradford.
OL,16,FWest Yorkshire Police said officers in
OL,17,Fa marked car saw the car driving at
OL,18,Fspeed on the opposite carriageway on
OL,19,FHalifax Road at about 8.25pm on
OL,20,FMonday, 16 September.
