OL,3,CTwo men arrested after teenager
OL,4,Ccritically injured in Bradford hit-and-
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FThey turned around to pursue the car
OL,8,Fbut lost sight of it.
OL,10,FA spokesperson said: "Officers then
OL,11,Flocated a pedestrian on Halifax Road
OL,12,Fwho had been hit by the suspect
OL,13,Fvehicle which had failed to stop at
OL,14,Fthe scene."
OL,16,FTwo 33-year-old men have been
OL,17,Farrested, one on suspicion of causing
OL,18,Fserious injury by dangerous driving
OL,19,Fand leaving the scene. The other was
OL,20,Farrested on suspicion of assisting an
OL,21,Foffender.
